responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "A890C2BE480A3CB7110853A2083B83D2", "If I wear the crown it shall grant me the power to control the most primitive of goblinoids. This will allow me to control territory through their savagery. I, the Master of Mungle, will lead them through fear, but I shall never allow them to see the true me. I will give life to a false goblinoid demigod and strike fear to the bone within them. Soon all shall carve a kingdom in the moors fitting of the arcane power of I, Maldore the Master of Mungle!")
name: MIDD_0020_MOM_Book_WizardJournal_9
